assets.name: Aquamax Hazer
assets.description: 100% certified organic haze without the residue associated with oil-based hazers. The AquaMax has built in fans to help spread the healthiest haze on earth, while remaining extremely conservative on fluid usage. This machine produces the smallest particles, which makes it extremely dry. Made in the USA
